OL,3,CElderly residents 'too scared to leave
OL,4,Chome' amid lift and stairlift issues
OL,6,FPeople who live in a block of flats
OL,7,Fsay they are worried about leaving
OL,8,Ftheir homes after repeated problems
OL,9,Fwith the lift as well a new stairlift.
OL,11,FSome residents, aged between 50 and
OL,12,F102, at Linden Court in Hampshire were
OL,13,Ftrapped over Christmas when the only
OL,14,Flift in the building broke down.
OL,16,FIn the last few weeks the lift has
OL,17,Fbeen fixed and a stairlift has been
OL,18,Finstalled, but people have told ITV
OL,19,FNews Meridian they are too scared to
OL,20,Fuse the lift in case it breaks down
OL,21,Fagain.
