OL,3,CElderly residents 'too scared to leave
OL,4,Chome' amid lift and stairlift issues
OL,6,FThey say because there is no handrail,
OL,7,Fpeople who lack mobility cannot move
OL,8,Facross the landing to get from one
OL,9,Ffrom stairlift to the other.
OL,11,FThere are also no remote controls to
OL,12,Faccess the stairlift, which is
OL,13,Fcurrently stranded halfway down the
OL,14,Fstaircase.
OL,16,FTom Proctor's father Frank turned 102
OL,17,Fat the beginning of January and he
OL,18,Fworries about not only his ability to
OL,19,Fget down the stairs and to the world
OL,20,Fbeyond, but also about his father's
OL,21,Fneighbours.
