OL,3,CElderly residents 'too scared to leave
OL,4,Chome' amid lift and stairlift issues
OL,6,FHe said: "They're scared to get into
OL,7,Fthe lift as they know it could break
OL,8,Fdown at any moment...Just like the
OL,9,Fperiod over Christmas, they're still
OL,10,Feffectively trapped."
OL,12,FAfter spending the festive period
OL,13,Falone because of the broken lift,
OL,14,Ffriends and family gathered to make
OL,15,Fsure he could make it to his own
OL,16,Fbirthday party.
OL,18,FFrank has 14 great grandchildren and
OL,19,Fwas awarded the Burma Star medal for
OL,20,Fhis work in the RAF during World War
OL,21,FII.
