OL,3,CElderly residents 'too scared to leave
OL,4,Chome' amid lift and stairlift issues
OL,6,FJanet Houghton, who is in her 90s, has
OL,7,Fnot left her apartment in days after
OL,8,Fshe fell face first out of the lift
OL,9,Fwhen it did not stop level with the
OL,10,Ffloor.
OL,12,FShe suffered facial bruising and cuts
OL,13,Fto her knees.
OL,15,FDescribing the experience, she told
OL,16,FITV News Meridian: "The doors opened
OL,17,Fas normal and I didn't notice that it
OL,18,Fwasn't quite level.
OL,20,F"I just went to walk straight out and
OL,21,Fcaught my foot and it send me flying."
