OL,3,CElderly residents 'too scared to leave
OL,4,Chome' amid lift and stairlift issues
OL,6,FSteven Dennis, the chief executive of
OL,7,FSaxon Weald, which owns and runs the
OL,8,Fbuilding, said the company was going
OL,9,Fto install new handrails today as well
OL,10,Fas put remote controls onto walls.
OL,12,FIn a statement, he said: "We act
OL,13,Fpromptly whenever residents raise a
OL,14,Fsafety concern. In this case, we only
OL,15,Fheard from a resident yesterday that
OL,16,Fthey were worried about the stairlift
OL,17,Fand have already taken further action.
