OL,3,CElderly residents 'too scared to leave
OL,4,Chome' amid lift and stairlift issues
OL,6,F"We can confirm that the stairlifts
OL,7,Fhave been installed by experienced
OL,8,Fprofessionals and meet all health and
OL,9,Fsafety requirements.
OL,11,F"However, we are happy to provide a
OL,12,Fhandrail to give residents extra
OL,13,Fsupport in crossing the small landing
OL,14,Fand this will be installed today.
OL,16,F"Four remote controls were provided,
OL,17,Fbut these now appear to be missing. We
OL,18,Fwere alerted of this yesterday and
OL,19,Fwill be taking more controllers to the
OL,20,Fscheme today.
