OL,3,CElderly residents 'too scared to leave
OL,4,Chome' amid lift and stairlift issues
OL,6,F"We will secure them to the wall so
OL,7,Fthat they cannot be lost or removed.
OL,9,F"We are very happy to arrange a
OL,10,Fdemonstration for anyone who doesn't
OL,11,Ffeel confident in using the stairlift
OL,12,Fand will contact all residents to ask
OL,13,Fif they are interested.
OL,15,F"In the meantime, the lift at Linden
OL,16,FCourt is fully working, so residents
OL,17,Fhave access to all floors."
